# Locally generated, secret-free CLI overlays (derived from a preset).
# Committed overlays use the bare `dbxcarta-overlay.env` name; any
# `*.local.env` / `*-overlay.local.env` is a transient generated artifact.
*.local.env
**/dbxcarta-overlay.local.env
# Standalone-submit example: the populated config is local-only. Only its
# .env.sample is committed; the filled-in submit_finance_genie.env never is.
examples/standalone-submit/submit_finance_genie.env
*.pem
*.key
*.crt
*.p12
secrets.json
secrets.yaml
secrets.yml
*_secret*
!setup_secrets.sh
*_credentials*

